{"tid":2358582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林建名病逝｜過千性伴食壯陽藥玩3P 台灣遭迷暈影裸照 17歲巴黎失身法國妹","createTime":"2021-01-08T08:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T11:38:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"709237cc07872477b4bea53e0ba472b276fd4166","tid":2358582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:41:25.000Z","msg":"大名娛樂老闆林建名今日因淋巴癌病逝，享年84歲 。他生前情史和性史皆成為城中熱話，雖然幾年前已經8字頭，但人到老年依然大把美女相伴，真係羨煞旁人。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前接受媒體訪問，他曾經大談自己的瘋狂性史，包括17歲失身、飛鵝山車震、食藥壯陽，講到興起時更自爆食女無數，笑認有過千性伴侶！<br />\n<br />\n關於「第一次」，林建名話地點喺巴黎，對象係法國妹：「第一年去英國讀書，暑假去巴黎玩。未識過女仔，朋友帶我去夜總會。有做，但冇高潮。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772732_0/%E6%9E%97%E5%BB%BA%E5%90%8D%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%83%E6%80%A7%E4%BC%B4%E9%A3%9F%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5%E7%8E%A93P-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%81%AD%E8%BF%B7%E6%9A%88%E5%BD%B1%E8%A3%B8%E7%85%A7-17%E6%AD%B2%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E5%A4%B1%E8%BA%AB%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%A6%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772732_0%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%2583%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25A3%25AF%25E9%2599%25BD%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%258E%25A93P-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%259A%2588%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25A3%25B8%25E7%2585%25A7-17%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A6%25B9&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=0490363b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772732_0%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%2583%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25A3%25AF%25E9%2599%25BD%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%258E%25A93P-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%259A%2588%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25A3%2